.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, azalea, sunflower, poppy, zinnia
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the chinese and the person who growszinnia##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the indian is the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
11. the indian is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Flower   | zinnia    | azalea       | sunflower      | begonia | poppy        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

