.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
There 5 different types of food: papaya, cabbage, asparagus, pineapple, pomegranate
 1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person watching crime movies and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the fisherman##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the pilot and the person eating cabbage##2
 7. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person eating asparagus##1
 9. the person eating papaya is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Food   | asparagus  | cabbage        | papaya   | pineapple    | pomegranate     |

